观看梦剧场 14 年来与迈克·波特诺伊 (Mike Portnoy) 合作的首场现场表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dream-theater-play-live-with-mike-portnoy-for-first-time-in-14-years-3804634?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= 14 年来第一次与迈克·波特诺伊一起观看梦剧院现场演出Tom SkinnerMon, 21 Oct 2024 09:47:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3804634 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="梦剧场的迈克·波特诺伊 (Mike Portnoy) 登台现场表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “梦剧院历史上非常特殊的时刻”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-dream-theater-play-live-with-mike-portnoy-for-first-time-in-14-years-3804634">《Watch Dream Theater》与 Mike Portnoy 14 年来首次现场演出的</a>帖子首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="梦剧场的迈克·波特诺伊 (Mike Portnoy) 登台现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/MikePortnoy-Dream-Theater-first-show-14-years-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（10 月 20 日），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dream-theater">梦剧院</a>与鼓手 Mike Portnoy 在伦敦进行了 14 年来的首场现场表演 - 请看下面的片段</p><p>据<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlist/dream-theater/2024/the-o2-arena-london-england-1bab6574.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Setlist.FM</em></a>报道，这支前卫金属乐队在首都 The O2 表演了 18 首歌曲，拉开了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dream-theater-announce-40th-anniversary-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3615300">他们 40 周年英国和欧洲巡演的序幕</a>。</p><p>音乐会分为两幕和一场安可，以播放“Metropolis Pt.”开始。 1: The Miracle And The Sleeper&#39; 选自梦剧场 1992 年专辑《Images And Words》，并以他们的经典单曲《Pull Me Under》的表演结束。</p><p>在其他地方，歌迷们还欣赏到了自 2014 年以来首度亮相的《The Mirror》以及新单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dream-theater-announce-new-album-parasomnia-with-technical-new-track-night-terror-3801722">《Night Terror》</a>的现场首演。此外，还有《Vacant》、《Stream Of Consciousness》、《Octavarium》和《Hollow Years》试玩版的罕见亮相。</p><p>在这次演出之前，波特诺伊自 2010 年 8 月起就没有在梦剧院演出过。</p><p>昨晚，这位音乐家还首次表演了“Barstool Warrior”和“This Is The Life”。这两首歌最初都是由迈克·曼吉尼（Mike Mangini）录制的，他取代了乐队阵容中的波特诺伊（Portnoy）。</p><p> “今晚是一个重要的时刻，”主唱詹姆斯·拉布里在演出中的某个时刻说道。 “你可能已经认出了舞台上的某个人。天哪——迈克·波特诺伊回来真是超现实！”</p><p>乐队在社交媒体上分享了两张音乐会照片，并写道：“今晚在梦剧院历史上创造了一个非常特殊的时刻，谢谢伦敦！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1ec-1f1e7.png" alt="🇬🇧" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ”。在演出开始前，波特诺伊发布了一张空 O2 的图片，并配上标题：“下一章今晚开始……”</p><p>请参阅下面的这些帖子、精选的粉丝拍摄视频以及完整的伦敦演出列表。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">今晚在梦剧场历史上创造了一个非常特别的时刻，谢谢伦敦！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f1ec-1f1e7.png" alt="🇬🇧" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4f8.png" alt="📸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://twitter.com/WorkByWolfe?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@WorkByWolfe</a> <a href="https://t.co/eMNpaX3LpD">pic.twitter.com/eMNpaX3LpD</a></p><p> - 梦剧场 (@dreamtheaternet) <a href="https://twitter.com/dreamtheaternet/status/1848152621665722500?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 10 月 21 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBWYZX7NRtm/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="no